Privacy Policy for BullViability

Last updated: 11.02.2026

BullViability is an independent mobile application designed to help users plan and visualize exit strategies for crypto assets.

1. Data Collection
The app may collect the following data:
- Email address (used solely for access control and authentication)
- App usage data (via Firebase Analytics)
- Crash and performance data (via Firebase Crashlytics)

No financial account data, wallet addresses, or private keys are collected.

2. Data Usage
Collected data is used only to:
- Provide access to the app
- Improve app stability and user experience
- Analyze anonymous usage patterns

3. Data Sharing
BullViability does not sell or share personal data with third parties.
Data is processed only by trusted services such as Google Firebase.

4. Data Storage & Security
Data is stored securely using industry-standard services.
Sensitive information is not exposed to other users.

5. User Rights
Users may request data removal by contacting the developer.

6. Children’s Privacy
This app is not intended for children under the age of 13.

7. Contact
